Interface CustomTabList

  • All Superinterfaces:
    TabList
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultTabList, SimpleTabList, TableTabList

    public interface CustomTabList
extends TabList
    Represents a tab list that can have custom and dynamic TabItem's.
